Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.46,0:00:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明与黑暗\N在陷入一片混乱的战国时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了四魂之玉\N因缘际会聚在一起的伙伴们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.77,0:00:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿越五百年的时光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.30,0:00:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最后仅存的四魂之玉碎片\N引导着各自的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.61,0:00:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战国时代的传奇故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.41,0:00:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此世与彼世的交界处\N沉睡着四魂之玉的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.08,0:00:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一一条通往彼世的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.81,0:00:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待我们的是\N守卫着火之国大门的巨大守门人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.52,0:00:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这里还有奈落设下的圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can now dream（勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.15,0:00:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.39,0:00:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a world（暧昧的世界）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.16,0:00:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋力冲出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.81,0:00:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对忧郁的现实生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.81,0:00:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断在心中自我成长的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.68,0:01:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜的梦境及梦中残留的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.82,0:01:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断断续续提醒我“勇往直前”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.06,0:01:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破茧而出的我  及含苞待放的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.77,0:01:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就将它禁锢起来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.81,0:01:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can now dream（勇敢的梦想）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.18,0:01:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥起舞动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.91,0:01:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go in and try（不顾一切的去尝试）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.28,0:01:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.28,0:01:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你天长地久永不分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.85,0:01:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need to cry（同样的哭泣）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孤独相伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Show me a day fight（直接应战）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.26,0:01:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当伤心流泪的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.36,0:01:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它成为坚定不移的梦想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.73,0:02:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我跟犬夜叉\N第一次遇见的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.37,0:02:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那却是战国时代的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.84,0:02:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.97,0:02:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.98,0:02:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这里\N应该就是我家附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是从这里开始的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在你身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我  好恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把四魂之玉交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百足妖妇\N这种杂碎你都对付不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.16,0:03:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚…说话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…你才应该要放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.04,0:03:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我啦\N快交出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.78,0:03:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你能拔掉这支箭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.25,0:03:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你能拔掉这支箭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.42,0:03:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种莫名其妙的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在这呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.21,0:04:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.38,0:04:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆  老太婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.41,0:04:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.76,0:04:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个时候\N我没有遭遇到妖怪的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.40,0:04:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又如果那个时候\N没有遇见犬夜叉的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我还在忙着准备考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.64,0:04:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也用不着在我跷课的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.64,0:04:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让爷爷帮我编各种的病名了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  好早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.08,0:04:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.55,0:04:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是以前的话\N绝对还赖在床上睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  便当做好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.29,0:04:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  好了\N都弄好了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.93,0:04:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.86,0:04:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.50,0:05:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.86,0:05:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要帮我问问\N他们吃了以后的感想喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.94,0:05:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个国中生来说\N光是读书就已经够累的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.44,0:05:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快点出发吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.95,0:05:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…今天还要去战国时代\N继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  欢迎你回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.34,0:05:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  犬夜叉  快点过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺回四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要继续努力寻找下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.72,0:06:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第145话\N那个世界的交界处  特异的守门人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到了吗  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.67,0:06:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.24,0:06:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最猛胜在监视着我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.38,0:06:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是某位大人物正在担心\N我们有没有真的去火之国吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.02,0:06:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的不知道\N其它去那的方法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去墓地的方法除此之外…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来告诉你们好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.84,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.47,0:06:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白童子那小鬼\N已经前往火之国的山了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.41,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一道\N通往此世与彼世交界处的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.62,0:07:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之国的山?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事  神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要告诉我们这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事你们去问白童子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.00,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这么看来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.37,0:07:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最猛胜可能是要引导我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此世与彼世交界处的大门吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.14,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方特地引导\N犬夜叉到那里去这件事看来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是因为\N以白童子的力量来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.65,0:07:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法通过那道门吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以奈落的性格来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.75,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定是有什么企图才会这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.72,0:07:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这次不是奈落\N而是白童子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白童子不就是奈落的分身吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是奈落也好  白童子也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.77,0:07:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只要我们抢先到那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把在所谓彼世与此世交界处的\N四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.90,0:07:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄到手不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个单纯的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.48,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说这样很像他的个性\N不如说他本性就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是火之国吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.36,0:08:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉上应该就是火之国没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.57,0:08:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在诱导我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.81,0:08:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿八  下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.55,0:08:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地底吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点令人毛骨悚然呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉上还真像是\N要通往墓地的入口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.70,0:08:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.31,0:09:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  犬夜叉他们已经\N顺利到达门的入口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.19,0:09:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗\N让犬夜叉他们先进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.29,0:09:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门的另一边\N不是有四魂之玉碎片吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.83,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然先得到四魂之玉碎片的\N一定是我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这个目的  神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要尽一份心力才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算等到最后\N坐享渔翁之利吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.20,0:09:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点跟奈落倒是一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必是因为那个门\N也是很大的缘故吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.09,0:09:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得那些石头\N很像妖怪的脸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像数量越来越多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.36,0:10:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是通往门的路上的铺石吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.87,0:10:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子我们终于到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.75,0:10:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有个门耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这扇门这么好找不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.16,0:10:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也没有烦人的守卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家退后一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用风之伤把这个门破坏掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.13,0:10:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想通过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.37,0:10:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁在这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.77,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答  你想通过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.61,0:10:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不想通过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要回答他\N犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.65,0:10:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟来了  冥加爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为他早就逃跑了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就要逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在还不会太迟\N快回头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.99,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说梦话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想通过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不想通过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是想通过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.43,0:11:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是为了通过\N才特地来到这里的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.41,0:11:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石…石像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个家伙是牛头跟马面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里的守门人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.18,0:12:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是装饰柱子的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.32,0:12:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有死者才能通过这扇门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.69,0:12:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何想通过这扇门的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.96,0:12:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须借由我们的手\N把他变成死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死就不能通过是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于知道白童子那个小鬼\N引导我们来这的原因了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.10,0:12:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过反正  我可不会因为这样\N就会有半点回去的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个家伙体型虽然庞大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是行动迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.28,0:12:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.02,0:12:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  我的风之伤居然没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.18,0:13:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此世的刀\N对我们起不了作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说\N此世的刀起不了作用是指…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为牛头马面\N根本就不属于此世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.95,0:13:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁碎牙终究是用来消灭\N此世的妖怪的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能伤得了牛头马面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去\N犬夜叉不就会被杀吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.43,0:13:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.80,0:13:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没有任何\N阻止牛头马面的方法了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛头马面一旦苏醒开始行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就非得把门打开\N再关上之后才会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.31,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要犬夜叉少爷变成死者\N通过这道门之后才有可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.98,0:13:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要通过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.35,0:13:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得成为死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能活着过去就没有意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想通过此世与彼世交界处的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.83,0:14:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须\N和守门人牛头马面交手才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.50,0:14:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.37,0:14:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在代替我跟他们战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.08,0:14:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久那道门就会开了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是以什么样的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是只有死者\N才能通过的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.35,0:14:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要用我们的手\N把你变成死者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.36,0:14:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的家伙\N只会重复同样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连一点裂痕都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.10,0:14:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.01,0:14:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.74,0:14:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此世的刀\N对我们是没有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  刀如果没有用的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.22,0:14:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想通过这道门吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风穴也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.55,0:15:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.19,0:15:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒\N就这样张开风穴不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把他弄倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.12,0:16:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借助风穴的力量发动攻击\N他们还是毫发无伤吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷  你还在这啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得人家没逃跑\N特意留在这的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.33,0:16:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦\N你有什么事情快点说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.73,0:16:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.97,0:16:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看先想办法让牛头马面\N恢复成他们原本石像的状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当门打开并且再关上的时候\N牛头马面就会停止行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只能赌赌看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.45,0:16:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准封住那道门的锁\N施展出风之伤把它砍碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.35,0:16:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了  我先失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还不是一样逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.26,0:16:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥加爷爷说的没有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果瞄准锁链一击\N就可以打开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一石二鸟之计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.47,0:16:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去打开结界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.18,0:16:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的铁碎牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.51,0:16:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.56,0:17:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.31,0:17:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先走一步啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.85,0:17:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.27,0:17:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.73,0:17:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.99,0:18:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪变成石头了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这些妖怪也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快躲开  会变成石头的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.53,0:18:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快躲起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.86,0:18:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在门的另一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.23,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想通过吗  还是不想通过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.47,0:19:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁想通过啊  混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把门关上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.68,0:19:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.79,0:19:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复成原来的石像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.96,0:20:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.63,0:20:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.53,0:20:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得白童子是不是早知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.24,0:20:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要穿过门的话\N就会变成石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.21,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拿我们投石问路\N连神乐也被利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白童子  你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我死了也无所谓是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.17,0:20:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是听说过活着的人\N不可能通过那道门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那是什么意思\N我就不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢耍我  臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.59,0:21:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吗  神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.93,0:21:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在奈落手里\N正握着你的心脏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在某个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好记住  神乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.97,0:21:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟奈落是紧紧相连的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.01,0:21:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次先想清楚这一点之后\N再采取行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.68,0:21:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.28,0:21:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭你这点功力根本就杀不了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.79,0:21:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.49,0:21:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.46,0:21:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当那道门打开的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.06,0:21:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边散发出\N四魂之玉碎片的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.90,0:21:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  真的在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.34,0:21:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片\N就在彼世的某个地方…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.16,0:22:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今内心充满着悲伤的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.17,0:22:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管靠着我哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.26,0:22:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像现在这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.67,0:23:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come my way 这点黑暗之尘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.71,0:23:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come close to me 现在灯已照亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.19,0:23:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是简简单单的陪在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.09,0:23:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们在火之国的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.92,0:23:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪竟然又开始大肆破坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.43,0:23:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟类好像受到控制\N开始袭击人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.93,0:23:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你也是奈落的爪牙
